    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "一、填空题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            61,
            134,
            150,
            149
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(1)【答案】 $-\\frac{1}{4}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            157,
            221,
            185
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 方法一",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            193,
            214,
            208
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $(1 + x)^{a} = 1 + ax + \\frac{a(a - 1)}{2!} x^{2} + o(x^{2})$ 得",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            215,
            489,
            243
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\sqrt {1 + x} = 1 + \\frac {1}{2} x - \\frac {1}{8} x ^ {2} + o (x ^ {2}), \\quad \\sqrt {1 - x} = 1 - \\frac {1}{2} x - \\frac {1}{8} x ^ {2} + o (x ^ {2}),\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            190,
            251,
            840,
            280
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "于是 $\\sqrt{1 + x} + \\sqrt{1 - x} - 2 = -\\frac{1}{4} x^2 + o(x^2) \\sim -\\frac{1}{4} x^2,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            289,
            582,
            318
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $\\lim_{x\\to 0}\\frac{\\sqrt{1 + x} + \\sqrt{1 - x} - 2}{x^2} = -\\frac{1}{4}.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            326,
            411,
            359
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "方法二",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            367,
            152,
            381
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\sqrt {1 + x} + \\sqrt {1 - x} - 2}{x ^ {2}} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\frac {1}{2 \\sqrt {1 + x}} - \\frac {1}{2 \\sqrt {1 - x}}}{2 x} \\\\ = \\frac {1}{4} \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {\\sqrt {1 - x} - \\sqrt {1 + x}}{x \\sqrt {1 - x ^ {2}}} = \\frac {1}{4} \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {- 2 x}{x (\\sqrt {1 + x} + \\sqrt {1 - x})} = - \\frac {1}{4}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            95,
            388,
            673,
            482
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 $yf''(xy) + \\varphi'(x + y) + y\\varphi''(x + y).$ ",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            488,
            477,
            504
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 $\\frac{\\partial z}{\\partial x} = -\\frac{1}{x^2} f(xy) + \\frac{y}{x} f'(xy) + y\\varphi'(x + y),$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            511,
            539,
            540
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\frac {\\partial^ {2} z}{\\partial x \\partial y} = - \\frac {1}{x} f ^ {\\prime} (x y) + \\frac {1}{x} f ^ {\\prime} (x y) + y f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (x y) + \\varphi^ {\\prime} (x + y) + y \\varphi^ {\\prime \\prime} (x + y) \\\\ = y f ^ {\\prime \\prime} (x y) + \\varphi^ {\\prime} (x + y) + y \\varphi^ {\\prime \\prime} (x + y). \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            547,
            700,
            601
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（3）【答案】 $12a$ ",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            605,
            206,
            621
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 由对称性得",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            627,
            252,
            641
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\oint_ {L} (2 x y + 3 x ^ {2} + 4 y ^ {2}) \\mathrm {d} s = \\oint_ {L} (3 x ^ {2} + 4 y ^ {2}) \\mathrm {d} s = 1 2 \\oint_ {L} \\left(\\frac {x ^ {2}}{4} + \\frac {y ^ {2}}{3}\\right) \\mathrm {d} s \\\\ = 1 2 \\oint_ {L} d s = 1 2 a. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            647,
            646,
            713
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(4)【答案】 $\\left(\\frac{|\\mathbf{A}|}{\\lambda}\\right)^2 + 1.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            719,
            285,
            748
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】设 $\\mathbf{A}$ 的对应于特征值 $\\lambda$ 的特征向量为 $\\alpha$ ，则 $A\\alpha = \\lambda \\alpha$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            756,
            595,
            771
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $\\mathbf{A}^{*}\\pmb {\\alpha} = \\frac{\\left|\\mathbf{A}\\right|}{\\lambda}\\pmb{\\alpha}$ 得 $[(\\mathbf{A}^{*})^{2} + \\mathbf{E}]\\pmb {\\alpha} = \\left[\\left(\\frac{\\left|\\mathbf{A}\\right|}{\\lambda}\\right)^{2} + 1\\right]\\pmb{\\alpha},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            775,
            572,
            807
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $(\\mathbf{A}^{*})^{2} + \\mathbf{E}$ 一定有特征值 $\\left(\\frac{|\\mathbf{A}|}{\\lambda}\\right)^2 +1.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            813,
            438,
            842
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(5)【答案】 $\\frac{1}{4}$ .",
        "bbox": [
            61,
            850,
            204,
            879
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 区域 $D$ 的面积为 $A = \\int_{1}^{\\mathrm{e}^{2}}\\mathrm{d}x\\int_{0}^{\\frac{1}{x}}\\mathrm{d}y = \\int_{1}^{\\mathrm{e}^{2}}\\frac{1}{x}\\mathrm{d}x = 2,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            883,
            572,
            915
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $(X,Y)$ 的联合密度为",
        "bbox": [
            92,
            923,
            289,
            937
        ],
        "page_idx": 0
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nf (x, y) = \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l l} \\frac {1}{2}, & (x, y) \\in D, \\\\ 0, & (x, y) \\notin D. \\end{array} \\right.\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            369,
            71,
            634,
            121
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $x \\leqslant 1$ 或 $x \\geqslant \\mathrm{e}^2$ 时， $f_{X}(x) = 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            127,
            382,
            142
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "当 $1 < x < \\mathrm{e}^2$ 时， $f_{X}(x) = \\int_{0}^{\\frac{1}{x}}\\frac{1}{2}\\mathrm{d}y = \\frac{1}{2x},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            149,
            448,
            179
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $f_{X}(2) = \\frac{1}{4}$ . ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            189,
            216,
            215
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "二、选择题",
        "text_level": 1,
        "bbox": [
            49,
            222,
            138,
            237
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（1）【答案】 （A).",
        "bbox": [
            49,
            244,
            198,
            258
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】由 $\\int_0^x tf(x^2 -t^2)\\mathrm{d}t = -\\frac{1}{2}\\int_0^x f(x^2 -t^2)\\mathrm{d}(x^2 -t^2)\\frac{x^2 - t^2 = u}{2}\\frac{1}{2}\\int_0^{x^2}f(u)\\mathrm{d}u,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            265,
            803,
            295
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $\\frac{\\mathrm{d}}{\\mathrm{d}x}\\int_{0}^{x}tf(x^2 -t^2)\\mathrm{d}t = xf(x^2)$ ，应选(A).",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            302,
            442,
            331
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(2)【答案】 (B).",
        "bbox": [
            49,
            338,
            196,
            354
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】 由 $\\lim_{x\\to -1}\\frac{f(x) - f(-1)}{x + 1} = \\lim_{x\\to -1}\\frac{(x + 1)(x - 2)\\mid x^3 - x\\mid}{x + 1}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            360,
            611,
            388
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n= \\lim  _ {[ - ]} (x - 2) \\mid x ^ {3} - x \\mid = 0,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            332,
            395,
            582,
            414
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "得 $f^{\\prime}(-1) = 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            419,
            221,
            434
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {f (x) - f (0)}{x - 0} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0} \\frac {| x |}{x} \\cdot (x ^ {2} - x - 2) | x ^ {2} - 1 |,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            439,
            543,
            468
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "显然 $f_{-}^{\\prime}(0) = \\lim_{x\\to 0^{-}}\\frac{|x|}{x}\\cdot (x^{2} - x - 2)|x^{2} - 1| = 2,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            475,
            539,
            507
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nf _ {+} ^ {\\prime} (0) = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 0 ^ {+}} \\frac {| x |}{x} \\cdot (x ^ {2} - x - 2) | x ^ {2} - 1 | = - 2,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            119,
            511,
            557,
            543
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $f_{-}^{\\prime}(0) \\neq f_{+}^{\\prime}(0)$ ，所以 $x = 0$ 为不可导的点；",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            547,
            500,
            562
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 1} \\frac {f (x) - f (1)}{x - 1} = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 1} \\frac {| x - 1 |}{x - 1} \\cdot (x ^ {2} - x - 2) | x (x + 1) |,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            569,
            601,
            597
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "显然 $f_{-}^{\\prime}(1) = \\lim_{x\\to 1^{-}}\\frac{|x - 1|}{x - 1}\\cdot (x^{2} - x - 2)\\mid x(x + 1)\\mid = 4,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            605,
            597,
            634
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nf _ {+} ^ {\\prime} (1) = \\lim  _ {x \\rightarrow 1 ^ {+}} \\frac {| x - 1 |}{x - 1} \\cdot (x ^ {2} - x - 2) | x (x + 1) | = - 4,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            119,
            641,
            617,
            670
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $f_{-}^{\\prime}(1) \\neq f_{+}^{\\prime}(1)$ ，所以 $x = 1$ 为不可导的点，即 $f(x)$ 有2个不可导的点，应选(B).",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            677,
            803,
            692
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "(3)【答案】 (D).",
        "bbox": [
            49,
            699,
            198,
            713
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】由 $\\Delta y = \\frac{y\\Delta x}{1 + x^2} +\\alpha$ 得 $y = y(x)$ 可微，从而 $y = y(x)$ 可导，",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            721,
            654,
            748
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "且 $\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}} = \\frac{y}{1 + x^2}$ 或 $\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dx}} -\\frac{1}{1 + x^2} y = 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            756,
            404,
            785
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "解得 $y = C\\mathrm{e}^{-\\int \\frac{-1}{1 + x^2}\\mathrm{d}x} = C\\mathrm{e}^{\\arctan x},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            793,
            355,
            818
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $y(0) = \\pi$ 得 $C = \\pi$ ，于是 $y(x) = \\pi \\mathrm{e}^{\\arctan x}$ 故 $y(1) = \\pi \\mathrm{e}^{\\frac{\\pi}{4}}$ ，应选(D).",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            827,
            669,
            849
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（4）【答案】 （A）.",
        "bbox": [
            49,
            854,
            198,
            869
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】因为 $\\left| \\begin{array}{lll}a_{1} & b_{1} & c_{1}\\\\ a_{2} & b_{2} & c_{2}\\\\ a_{3} & b_{3} & c_{3} \\end{array} \\right| = \\left| \\begin{array}{ccc}a_{1} - a_{2} & b_{1} - b_{2} & c_{1} - c_{2}\\\\ a_{2} - a_{3} & b_{2} - b_{3} & c_{2} - c_{3}\\\\ a_{3} & b_{3} & c_{3} \\end{array} \\right|\\neq 0,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            875,
            609,
            934
        ],
        "page_idx": 1
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "所以两条直线的方向向量不平行，（B）与（C）不对；",
        "bbox": [
            78,
            67,
            493,
            82
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $s_1 = \\{a_1 - a_2, b_1 - b_2, c_1 - c_2\\}$ , $s_2 = \\{a_2 - a_3, b_2 - b_3, c_2 - c_3\\}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            78,
            89,
            659,
            105
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$M_{1}(a_{3},b_{3},c_{3}),M_{2}(a_{1},b_{1},c_{1})$ 分别为两条直线上的点，",
        "bbox": [
            78,
            112,
            530,
            125
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\overrightarrow {M _ {1} M _ {2}} = \\left\\{a _ {1} - a _ {3}, b _ {1} - b _ {3}, c _ {1} - c _ {3} \\right\\},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            78,
            132,
            388,
            150
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $\\overrightarrow{M_1M_2} \\cdot (\\pmb{s}_1 \\times \\pmb{s}_2) = \\left| \\begin{array}{ccc} a_1 - a_3 & b_1 - b_3 & c_1 - c_3 \\\\ a_1 - a_2 & b_1 - b_2 & c_1 - c_2 \\\\ a_2 - a_3 & b_2 - b_3 & c_2 - c_3 \\end{array} \\right| = 0$ ，所以两直线共面且不平行，即两直线交于一点，应选(A).",
        "bbox": [
            78,
            157,
            923,
            239
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "（5）【答案】 (C).",
        "bbox": [
            49,
            246,
            198,
            262
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "【解】由 $P(B\\mid A) = P(B\\mid \\overline{A})$ 得 $\\frac{P(AB)}{P(A)} = \\frac{P(\\overline{A}B)}{P(\\overline{A})}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            78,
            266,
            547,
            302
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由减法公式及补概率的公式得 $\\frac{P(AB)}{P(A)} = \\frac{P(B) - P(AB)}{1 - P(A)}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            309,
            561,
            338
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "整理得 $P(AB) = P(A)P(B)$ ，应选(C).",
        "bbox": [
            80,
            347,
            413,
            360
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "三、【解】 方法一 $L$ 的参数方程为 $L:\\left\\{ \\begin{array}{ll}x = 1 + t,\\\\ y = t,\\\\ z = 1 - t, \\end{array} \\right.$ 代入 $\\pi$ 得 $L$ 与 $\\pi$ 的交点为 $M_{1}(2,1,0)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            49,
            369,
            797,
            424
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$M_0(1,0,1)\\in L$ ，过 $M_0$ 且与 $\\pi$ 垂直的直线为 $L^{\\prime}$ ： $\\frac{x - 1}{1} = \\frac{y}{-1} = \\frac{z - 1}{2},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            434,
            669,
            461
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$L^{\\prime}$ 的参数方程为 $L^{\\prime}$ $\\begin{cases} x = 1 + t,\\\\ y = -t,\\\\ z = 1 + 2t, \\end{cases}$ 代入 $\\pi$ 得垂足坐标为 $M_2\\left(\\frac{2}{3},\\frac{1}{3},\\frac{1}{3}\\right)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            470,
            679,
            526
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$\\overrightarrow{M_2M_1} = \\left\\{\\frac{4}{3},\\frac{2}{3}, - \\frac{1}{3}\\right\\}$ 故 $L_{0}: \\frac{x - 2}{4} = \\frac{y - 1}{2} = \\frac{z}{-1}.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            535,
            543,
            562
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "设 $L_{0}$ 绕 $y$ 轴旋转一周所得的旋转曲面为 $\\Sigma$ ，任取 $P(x,y,z)\\in \\Sigma$ ，其所在的圆周对应的 $L_{0}$ 上的点为 $P_0(x_0,y,z_0)$ ，圆心为 $T(0,y,0)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            571,
            925,
            608
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $|PT| = |P_0T|$ 得 $x^{2} + z^{2} = x_{0}^{2} + z_{0}^{2}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            76,
            615,
            427,
            630
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "再由 $P_{0}(x_{0},y,z_{0})\\in L_{0}$ 得 $\\frac{x_0 - 2}{4} = \\frac{y - 1}{2} = \\frac{z_0}{-1}$ 解得 $x_0 = 2y,z_0 = -\\frac{y - 1}{2}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            74,
            640,
            747,
            666
        ],
        "page_idx": 2
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $\\Sigma$ 的方程为 $4x^{2} - 17y^{2} + 4z^{2} + 2y - 1 = 0.$ ",
