    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "直线 $L: \\frac{x - 1}{1} = \\frac{y}{1} = \\frac{z - 1}{-1}$ 的一般形式为 $L: \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} \\frac{x - 1}{1} = \\frac{y}{1}, \\\\ \\frac{y}{1} = \\frac{z - 1}{-1}, \\end{array} \\right.$ $L: \\left\\{ \\begin{array}{l} x - y - 1 = 0, \\\\ y + z - 1 = 0, \\end{array} \\right.$ ",
