    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "再由 $P_{0}(x_{0},y,z_{0})\\in L_{0}$ 得 $\\frac{x_0 - 2}{4} = \\frac{y - 1}{2} = \\frac{z_0}{-1}$ 解得 $x_0 = 2y,z_0 = -\\frac{y - 1}{2}$ ",
