    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\frac {\\partial P}{\\partial y} = 2 x \\left(x ^ {4} + y ^ {2}\\right) ^ {\\lambda} + 4 \\lambda x y ^ {2} \\left(x ^ {4} + y ^ {2}\\right) ^ {\\lambda - 1},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
