        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $\\frac{\\partial P}{\\partial y} = \\frac{\\partial Q}{\\partial x}$ 得 $4x(\\lambda + 1)(x^4 + y^2) = 0$ ，解得 $\\lambda = -1$ ",
        "bbox": [
