        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $u(x,y) = \\int_{(1,0)}^{(x,y)}\\frac{2xy\\mathrm{d}x - x^2\\mathrm{d}y}{x^4 + y^2} = \\int_1^x 0\\mathrm{d}x + \\int_0^y\\frac{-x^2\\mathrm{d}y}{x^4 + y^2} = -\\arctan \\frac{y}{x^2} +C,$ ",
        "bbox": [
