        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故所求的二元函数为 $u(x,y) = -\\arctan \\frac{y}{x^2} +C(C$ 为任意常数).",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            403,
            626,
            428
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "五、【解】 取沉放点为坐标原点， $y$ 轴铅直向下，由牛顿第二定律得",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            435,
            605,
            450
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\nm \\frac {\\mathrm {d} ^ {2} y}{\\mathrm {d} t ^ {2}} = m g - B \\rho - k v,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            409,
