            619,
            488
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $\\frac{\\mathrm{dy}}{\\mathrm{dt}} = v$ ，则 $\\frac{\\mathrm{d}^2y}{\\mathrm{d}t^2} = v\\frac{\\mathrm{d}v}{\\mathrm{d}y}$ 代人得 $\\frac{mv\\mathrm{d}v}{\\mathrm{d}y} = mg - B\\rho -kv$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
