        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "变量分离得 $\\frac{mv\\mathrm{d}v}{mg - B\\rho - kv} = \\mathrm{dy}$ ，积分得",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            535,
            423,
            562
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\ny = - \\frac {m}{k} v - \\frac {m (m g - B \\rho)}{k ^ {2}} \\ln (m g - B \\rho - k v) + C _ {0},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            299,
            571,
            729,
            600
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $y|_{t = 0} = 0, v|_{t = 0} = 0$ 得 $C_0 = \\frac{m(mg - B\\rho)}{k^2}\\ln (mg - B\\rho)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            609,
            601,
            637
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $y = -\\frac{m}{k} v - \\frac{m(mg - B\\rho)}{k^2}\\ln \\frac{mg - B\\rho - kv}{mg - B\\rho}.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            647,
            483,
            677
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "六、【解】 $I = \\iint_{\\Sigma} \\frac{ax \\, \\mathrm{d}y \\, \\mathrm{d}z + (z + a)^2 \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y}{\\sqrt{x^2 + y^2 + z^2}} = \\frac{1}{a} \\iint_{\\Sigma} ax \\, \\mathrm{d}y \\, \\mathrm{d}z + (z + a)^2 \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            64,
            684,
            688,
            717
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $\\Sigma_0: z = 0 (x^2 + y^2 \\leqslant a^2)$ ，取下侧，则",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            724,
            423,
            739
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\iint_ {\\Sigma} a x \\mathrm {d} y \\mathrm {d} z + (z + a) ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y = \\iint_ {\\Sigma + \\Sigma_ {0}} a x \\mathrm {d} y \\mathrm {d} z + (z + a) ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y - \\iint_ {\\Sigma_ {0}} a x \\mathrm {d} y \\mathrm {d} z + (z + a) ^ {2} \\mathrm {d} x \\mathrm {d} y,\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            746,
            809,
            782
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "而 $\\iint_{\\Sigma + \\Sigma_0} ax \\, \\mathrm{d}y \\, \\mathrm{d}z + (z + a)^2 \\, \\mathrm{d}x \\, \\mathrm{d}y = -\\iiint_{\\Omega} (2z + 3a) \\, \\mathrm{d}v = -2\\iiint_{\\Omega} z \\, \\mathrm{d}v - 3a \\cdot \\frac{2}{3}\\pi a^3$ ",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            786,
            729,
            822
        ],
        "page_idx": 3
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} = - 2 \\int_ {0} ^ {2 \\pi} d \\theta \\int_ {\\frac {\\pi}{2}} ^ {\\pi} d \\varphi \\int_ {0} ^ {a} r ^ {3} \\sin \\varphi \\cos \\varphi d r - 2 \\pi a ^ {4} \\\\ = \\frac {\\pi a ^ {4}}{2} - 2 \\pi a ^ {4} = - \\frac {3 \\pi a ^ {4}}{2}; \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            90,
            786,
