    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "故 $I = \\frac{1}{a}\\left(-\\frac{3\\pi a^4}{2} + \\pi a^4\\right) = -\\frac{1}{2}\\pi a^3.$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            71,
            413,
