        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "七、【解】 $b_{n} = \\frac{\\sin\\frac{\\pi}{n}}{n + 1} +\\frac{\\sin\\frac{2\\pi}{n}}{n + \\frac{1}{2}} +\\dots +\\frac{\\sin\\frac{n\\pi}{n}}{n + \\frac{1}{n}},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            112,
