            171
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\frac {1}{n + 1} \\sum_ {i = 1} ^ {n} \\sin \\frac {\\pi i}{n} \\leqslant b _ {n} \\leqslant \\frac {1}{n} \\sum_ {i = 1} ^ {n} \\sin \\frac {\\pi i}{n},\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            357,
            181,
            665,
            211
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\frac{1}{n + 1}\\sum_{i = 1}^{n}\\sin \\frac{\\pi i}{n} = \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\frac{n}{n + 1}\\cdot \\frac{1}{n}\\sum_{i = 1}^{n}\\sin \\frac{\\pi i}{n} = \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\frac{1}{n}\\sum_{i = 1}^{n}\\sin \\frac{\\pi i}{n} = \\int_0^1\\sin \\pi x\\mathrm{d}x,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            221,
            783,
            251
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "所以由夹逼定理得",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            258,
            239,
            272
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n\\begin{array}{l} \\lim  _ {n \\rightarrow \\infty} \\left(\\frac {\\sin \\frac {\\pi}{n}}{n + 1} + \\frac {\\sin \\frac {2 \\pi}{n}}{n + \\frac {1}{2}} + \\dots + \\frac {\\sin \\frac {n \\pi}{n}}{n + \\frac {1}{n}}\\right) = \\int_ {0} ^ {1} \\sin \\pi x d x = \\frac {1}{\\pi} \\int_ {0} ^ {1} \\sin \\pi x d (\\pi x) \\\\ = \\frac {1}{\\pi} \\int_ {0} ^ {\\pi} \\sin x d x = \\frac {2}{\\pi}. \\\\ \\end{array}\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            282,
            681,
            378
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "八、【解】因为 $\\{a_{n}\\}$ 单调递减且 $a_{n} > 0$ ，所以 $\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}a_n$ 存在，设 $\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}a_n = A$ ，显然 $A\\geqslant 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            388,
            756,
            410
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为交错级数 $\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}(-1)^{n}a_{n}$ 发散且 $\\{a_{n}\\}$ 单调递减，所以 $A > 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            414,
            597,
            446
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "对正项级数 $\\sum_{n=1}^{\\infty}\\left(\\frac{1}{a_n + 1}\\right)^n$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            453,
            311,
            485
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $\\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\sqrt[n]{\\left(\\frac{1}{a_n + 1}\\right)^n} = \\lim_{n\\to \\infty}\\frac{1}{a_n + 1} = \\frac{1}{A + 1} < 1$ ，所以级数 $\\sum_{n = 1}^{\\infty}\\left(\\frac{1}{a_n + 1}\\right)^n$ 收敛.",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            493,
            747,
            526
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "九、【证明】 $(1)S_{1}(x_{0}) = x_{0}f(x_{0}),\\quad S_{2}(x_{0}) = \\int_{x_{0}}^{1}f(x)\\mathrm{d}x,$ ",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            535,
            574,
            565
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "令 $\\varphi (x) = xf(x) - \\int_{x}^{1}f(t)\\mathrm{d}t$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            569,
            345,
            594
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "显然 $F(x) = x\\int_{x}^{x}f(t)\\mathrm{d}t$ 为 $\\varphi (x)$ 的原函数，即 $F^{\\prime}(x) = \\varphi (x)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            605,
            615,
            630
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "$F(0) = F(1) = 0$ ，由罗尔定理，存在 $x_0\\in (0,1)$ ，使得 $F^{\\prime}(x_0) = 0$ ，即 $\\varphi (x_0) = 0$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
