        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "equation",
        "text": "$$\n(2) \\varphi^ {\\prime} (x) = f (x) + x f ^ {\\prime} (x) + f (x) = x f ^ {\\prime} (x) + 2 f (x),\n$$",
        "text_format": "latex",
        "bbox": [
            88,
            687,
            572,
            701
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $f^{\\prime}(x) > - \\frac{2f(x)}{x}$ 得 $xf^{\\prime}(x) + 2f(x) > 0$ ，即 $\\varphi '(x) > 0(0 <   x <   1)$ ",
        "bbox": [
