        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "则 $\\varphi (x)$ 在(0，1）内严格递增，故（1）中的 $x_0$ 是唯一的",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            746,
            537,
            760
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "十、【解】 令 $\\mathbf{A} = \\begin{pmatrix} 1 & b & 1 \\\\ b & a & 1 \\\\ 1 & 1 & 1 \\end{pmatrix}, \\mathbf{X} = \\begin{pmatrix} x \\\\ y \\\\ z \\end{pmatrix}$ ，则二次曲面表示为 $\\mathbf{X}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\mathbf{A}\\mathbf{X} = 4$ ",
        "bbox": [
            59,
            771,
            659,
            824
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "因为 $\\mathbf{X}^{\\mathrm{T}}\\mathbf{A}\\mathbf{X}$ 经过正交变换可以化为 $\\eta^2 +4\\xi^2$ ，所以矩阵 $\\mathbf{A}$ 的特征值为 $\\lambda_1 = 0,\\lambda_2 = 1,\\lambda_3 = 4$ 由 $\\operatorname {tr}\\mathbf{A} = \\lambda_{1} + \\lambda_{2} + \\lambda_{3}$ 得 $a + 2 = 5$ ，解得 $a = 3$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            834,
            849,
            869
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $|\\mathbf{A}| = \\lambda_1\\lambda_2\\lambda_3$ 得 $b = 1$ ，即 $\\mathbf{A} = \\begin{pmatrix} 1 & 1 & 1\\\\ 1 & 3 & 1\\\\ 1 & 1 & 1 \\end{pmatrix} .$ ",
        "bbox": [
            86,
            882,
            475,
            934
        ],
        "page_idx": 4
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $0E - A \\rightarrow \\left( \\begin{array}{ccc}1 & 0 & 1\\\\ 0 & 1 & 0\\\\ 0 & 0 & 0 \\end{array} \\right)$ 得 $\\lambda_{1} = 0$ 对应的特征向量为 $\\pmb{\\alpha}_{1} = \\left( \\begin{array}{c} - 1\\\\ 0\\\\ 1 \\end{array} \\right)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            71,
            646,
            127
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $\\pmb {E} - \\pmb {A}\\rightarrow \\left( \\begin{array}{lll}1 & 0 & -1\\\\ 0 & 1 & 1\\\\ 0 & 0 & 0 \\end{array} \\right)$ 得 $\\lambda_{2} = 1$ 对应的特征向量为 $\\pmb{\\alpha}_{2} = \\left( \\begin{array}{l}1\\\\ -1\\\\ 1 \\end{array} \\right)$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            134,
            652,
            190
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "由 $4\\pmb {E} - \\pmb {A}\\rightarrow \\left( \\begin{array}{rrr}1 & 0 & -1\\\\ 0 & 1 & -2\\\\ 0 & 0 & 0 \\end{array} \\right)$ 得 $\\lambda_3 = 4$ 对应的特征向量为 $\\alpha_{3} = \\binom{1}{2}$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            197,
            642,
            251
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "规范化得 $\\gamma_{1} = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}}\\binom{-1}{0},\\quad \\gamma_{2} = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{3}}\\binom{1}{-1},\\quad \\gamma_{3} = \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{6}}\\binom{1}{2},$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            260,
            586,
            313
        ],
        "page_idx": 5
    },
    {
        "type": "text",
        "text": "得正交矩阵 $\\pmb{P} = \\left[ \\begin{array}{ccc} - \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}} & \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{3}} & \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{6}}\\\\ 0 & -\\frac{1}{\\sqrt{3}} & \\frac{2}{\\sqrt{6}}\\\\ \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{2}} & \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{3}} & \\frac{1}{\\sqrt{6}} \\end{array} \\right].$ ",
        "bbox": [
            84,
            320,
            404,
            434
        ],
